          	  			<p data-element="content" class="content">For a night out on the town, it&#8217;s tempting to grab that little black dress out of the closet to strut your best stuff.  &quot;While a little black dress can be a great and versatile addition to your evening wear, it's not the end-all and be-all of dressing after dark,&quot; says Dianne Daniels, a Connecticut-based image consultant. Spruce up your style and your evening wear with colorful and stylish alternatives to the LBD.</p>
